TITLE: Kalki Avatar | Experience With Maa Adi Parashakti Noor Ananta's Energy | Anish Kumar
VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f4HvIX84dF0
LANGUAGE: Hindi (auto-translated)

SUMMARY:
Anish Kumar shares his experience of being connected to the Adi Parashakti Noor Ananta WhatsApp channel from the very beginning. He describes significant transformation since joining, particularly through following the "dark side awareness" techniques that Maa taught. He took the guidance seriously, and even though he faced setbacks and had disagreements with the group admins, he took everything positively as a learning opportunity.

He describes a growing sense of love within himself and explains that as he goes deeper into observing his dark side, an increasingly intense vibration emerges from within. He encourages others to develop their energy sensitivity to understand Maa's aura, which he describes as a white-colored aura similar to that emanating from a goddess temple. He notes his natural ability to read people through their eyes, which helped him recognize Maa's authenticity and the genuine spiritual energy (chaspta) present in her.

KEY REVELATIONS:
- Connected from the beginning of the WhatsApp channel and witnessed significant personal transformation
- Practiced "dark side awareness" technique taught by Maa with serious dedication
- Perceives Maa's aura as white-colored, similar to the aura from a goddess temple
- Experienced growing inner vibrations and love as he goes deeper into self-awareness
- Has natural ability to read people through their eyes, which confirmed Maa's authenticity

YUG PARIVARTAN ASPECT: Energy Activation

